title: H-Street - Hokus Pokus [1989][skateboarding] DVDrip.avi
description:
In 1989 came this world-renowned film that sold more copies than any other skateboard film. Hokus pokus reflects H-street at it's best, while skateboarding was on top. Still filmed with inexpensive cameras and edited in the living room, Hokus Pokus made history with the skating from Matt Hensley, Sal Barbier, Danny Way, Mike Carroll, Alphonzo Rawls, Ron Allen, Jason Rogers, John Shultes, John Sonner, Colby Carter, Tony Magnusson, Brian Lotti, Dave Donalson, John Reeves, Aaron Vincent, John De Ago, Donger, Steve Ortega, Ray Simmonds, Kit Erickson, Josh Swindell, Brennand Schoeffel, Chris Livingston, Eddie Elguera, Art Godoy, Jeff Petit, Noah Salasnek,Darin Jenkins, Ocean Howell, Marcus Wyndham, Dan Peterka and many other great skaters.
